description: Discover this light-filled 2 bed / 2 bath corner residence at the desirable Park Millennium. Floor-to-ceiling windows showcase sweeping city and park views,  filling the home with natural light and creating an uplifting atmosphere - making even rainy or snowy days feel special. The open living and dining space perfect for entertaining or cozy nights in, while the modern kitchen, spacious bedrooms and in-unit laundry make everyday living comfortable and practical. At Park Millennium, resort-style amenities make city living effortless: swim laps in the indoor pool, relax in the hot tub or sauna, work out in the expansive gym, or enjoy summer evenings grilling on the sundeck. The building also offers a business center, party room, 24-hour door staff, on-site dry cleaners, and direct connection to the Pedway system for easy all-weather access to shopping, dining, and public transportation. The Lakeshore East location is unbeatable, steps to Michigan Avenue, Millennium Park, Mariano's, Wildberry Cafe, the Riverwalk, lakefront paths, museums, theaters, and more. From morning coffee at a local cafe to evening strolls along the lake, this home puts the best of Chicago right outside your door. HOA includes heat, air, cable, internet, and amenities. Leased parking available. This is more than a condo, it's a lifestyle in one of Chicago's most vibrant and connected neighborhoods.
